 &gt;&gt; What are the contents of your $PATH environment variable?<br> &gt;&gt; Make sure that your Open-MPI folder<br> &gt;&gt; (/usr/lib/openmpi/1.2.5-gcc/bin)<br> &gt;&gt; precedes &#39;/usr/bin&#39; in $PATH,<br> &gt;&gt; i.e.<br>
 &gt;&gt; /usr/lib/openmpi/1.2.5-gcc/bin:/usr/bin<br> &gt;&gt;<br> &gt;&gt; then the Open-MPI version of mpirun or mpiexec will be used<br> &gt;&gt; instead of<br> &gt;&gt; the LAM-versions.<br> &gt;&gt;<br> &gt;&gt; This should also be the case on your other machines.<br>
